{{Added feature/item|1.5.9|1.5.8|21251|This function gets visibility of corona reflection.}}
==Syntax== 
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">
bool isCoronaReflectionEnabled ( marker theMarker )
</syntaxhighlight> 
{{OOP||[[Marker]]:isCoronaReflectionEnabled||setCoronaReflectionEnabled}}
===Required Arguments=== 
*'''theMarker:''' marker

===Returns===
* Returns ''false'' is [[setMarkerType|marker type]] is not ''corona''.
* Returns ''true'' if corona reflection is enabled, ''false'' otherwise.

